data.description: Situated on a spacious corner lot at the end of a peaceful cul-de-sac, this immaculate 4-bedroom traditional home is move-in ready—simply bring your furniture! With a brand-new 50-year roof recently installed, and a fresh coat of paint in this season's trending colors, all you need to do is add your personal touch. Enjoy leisurely evenings on the screened deck, ideal unwinding. Abundant storage solutions and a 2-car garage make it effortless to stow away your belongings and recreational items. Plus, there's no HOA to worry about. This residence is zoned for Yorktown's highly sought-after schools and conveniently located near NASA, the Coast Guard Station, Langley/Eustis Bases, as well as shopping, dining, and the beach just minutes away. Schedule a property tour today to explore all that this home has to offer!
